{"root":{"data":{"id":"div1intzi000","created":1780045644071,"text":"LLM"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3n0yz9vs0","created":1780051628347,"text":"Pytorch的TransformerAPI","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-51.999998450279406,"y":-587.9999824762351}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3n7xn4zs0","created":1780051643504,"text":"API"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3nzeqxwg0","created":1780051703311,"text":"nn.MultiheadAttention"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3o3qvjag0","created":1780051712752,"text":"nn.TransformerEncoderLayer"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3o6kcq3s0","created":1780051718888,"text":"nn.TransformerEncoder"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3oahxg140","created":1780051727448,"text":"nn.TransformerDecoderLayer"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3od1c7x40","created":1780051732976,"text":"nn.TransformerDecoder"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3ofv7rgg0","created":1780051739136,"text":"nn.Transformer"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div3oo43uy00","created":1780051757088,"text":"两种 Mask 的区别"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3orfg3j40","created":1780051764304,"text":"src_key_padding_mask / tgt_key_padding_mask / memory_key_padding_mask 的现状(batch_size, sequence_length)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3po6kxi00","created":1780051835601,"text":"src_mask / tgt_mask / memory_mask的现状(sequence_length, sequence_length)"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div3rbapssg0","created":1780051964282,"text":"位置编码"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3renrwhc0","created":1780051971602,"text":"正余弦位置编码"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3rqli8xs0","created":1780051997586,"text":"可学习位置编码"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3sf4nzcg0","created":1780052050987,"text":"外推性问题：可学习位置编码的软肋。可学习位置编码最⼤的局限在于⽆法外推。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3sjn9ms80","created":1780052060819,"text":"截断/重复。 将位置 映射回 或 ，但这样不同位置会共享编码，丢失区分度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3sqnbbv40","created":1780052076059,"text":"插值。 对 的⾏向量做线性插值，将 ⾏扩展到更⻓。但这只是近似，且插值⽅式缺\n乏理论保证。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3sxk1p400","created":1780052091099,"text":"位置缩放（Position Interpolation）。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div3tzxpops0","created":1780052174643,"text":"RoPE旋转位置编码"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3ukserlc0","created":1780052220035,"text":"也就是通过将位置信息以旋转矩阵的形式作⽤于 Query 和 Key 向量，使得内积结果⾃然包含相对位置信息。"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"div3xu0lels0","created":1780052475213,"text":"Hugging Face ⽣态概述","layout_mind_offset":{"x":863.4999587610371,"y":123.74999446794425}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3y67qsf40","created":1780052501767,"text":"核⼼组件","layout_right_offset":{"x":24.999998882412854,"y":-17.499999217688696}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div3yqaigpk0","created":1780052545470,"text":"Hub \n模型仓库，托管预训练模型/数据集"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3yw4h6y00","created":1780052558166,"text":"Transformers \n提供统⼀的模型 API（AutoModel / Trainer /\nPipeline）hugging face的核⼼"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3z1x484g0","created":1780052570782,"text":"Tokenizers \nRust 实现的快速分词后端，提供 word_ids /\noffset_mapping 等⾼级⽅法"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3za6xu680","created":1780052588790,"text":"Datasets \n数据集加载、处理、缓存"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div3zetjbyg0","created":1780052598863,"text":".........."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"div41odeqyo0","created":1780052776384,"text":"核⼼模块"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"div41uz7hsw0","created":1780052790763,"text":"AutoModel 系列"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div41ydqnps0","created":1780052798172,"text":"AutoTokenizer"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div423fny140","created":1780052809172,"text":"AutoConfig"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div426drgbk0","created":1780052815588,"text":"Trainer"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"div42b22f200","created":1780052825764,"text":"............."},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}